-class TimeTracker {
-  constructor(filePath: string)
-  start(taskName: string): Entry
-  stop(): Entry
-  getActiveTask(): Entry | null
-  getLog(options?: { since?: Date }): Entry[]
-  getSummary(): Record<string, number>
-}
-```
